comments: He is a genius and cares about student!

It\'s important to note that he\'s a good guy. The problem is that his thinking is not the same as his students. He really, really wants everyone to do well and he\'s happy to repeat himself but it is difficult to learn from him. He does have a sense of humor, though, and I like when applies things to the real world.
Highly recommended if you want an easy A. He provides sample tests that are nearly identical to the exams.
Good luck getting him to show up on time
